sentences: Bachchu Kailash (Nepali: बच्चु कैलाश) (born 30 July 1938) is a singer, composer and lyricist of Nepali Music.
Bachchu Kailash was born on Shawan 15, 1995 B. S (30 July 1938) in Sapatel, Chhorumbu VDC, Khotang.
Bachchu Kailash was born on Shawan 15, 1995 B. S (30 July 1938) in Sapatel, Chhorumbu VDC, Khotang.
On the 13th day, his mother died and his father Karna Bahadur Basnet remarried.
By the time he was five years old, he was already deep into music.
His performance that day became popular among the public and virtuoso Master Ratna Das Prakash, after listening to the song, became a fan and started looking for him.
He devoted his life to singing Nepali songs for about 15 years and his popularity remains undiminished.
These days, he is leading a happy and contented life away from the limelight.
Hridyama Bata Hunchhan, Tyahin Pani Bhet Hunchha
